                        <h2 class="usp-heading">Heatmaps</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                    <strong>Analyze newtork catch reports to target where the fish are.</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review catch data over past 7 days</li>
                    <li>View catches by location</li>
                    <li>Target specific species by location</li>
                    <li>Heatmap highlights where the bite is</li>
                    <li>Analyze catch patterns make informaed decisions</li>
                    <li>Reduce fuel expenses by targeting where the action is</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <!-- reports container  -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <a href="reports" class="list-group-item">
            <div class="panel-body bg-gray-light" style="height: 108px !important;">
                <div class="row vertical-align" style="margin-left: 0px!important; margin-right: 0px !important;">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
                        <%= image_tag 'hook.png', class: 'img-responsive usp-icon', style: 'display:block' %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-xs-8">
                        <h2 class="usp-heading">Daily Intel</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                    <strong>Daily reports from our network of charter/recreational captains and spotter pilots </strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>This is <strong>NOT</strong> report chasing</li>
                    <li>Stay informed with recent intel </li>
                    <li>Make informed decision on where the bite is moving </li>
                    <li>Activie community of fisherman who help each other</li>
                    <li>Stay current on trends that are working</li>
                    <li>Eliminate lifeless water by knowing where to avoid</li>  
                </ul>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <!-- Intel container -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
        <a href="buzzs" class="list-group-item">

            <div class="panel-heading bg-gray-light vertical-align" style="height: 108px !important;">
                <div class="row vertical-align" style="margin-left: 0px!important; margin-right: 0px!important;">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-4">
                        <%= image_tag 'binocs.png', class: 'img-responsive usp-icon', style: 'display:block' %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-xs-8">
                        <h2 class="usp-heading">Spotter Planes</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>
                    <strong>Weekly spotter plane intel to target where the fish are. We then pass along the exact GPS numbers of offshore fish schools, kelp paddies and more.</strong>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Numbers where schools are spotted</li>
                    <li>Aeriel photos</li>
                    <li>Gain advantage by knowing where the fish are</li>
                    <li>Eliminate Fuel costs</li>
                    <br>
                </ul>
            </div>

        </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

